              "code": "995373",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "样例说明",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "对于样例一，满足问题条件的整数对为 $(x,y) = (1,1), (1,3), (2,1), (2,2), (2,3), (3,1), (3,3)$，总共七对。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "例如，当 $(x,y) = (2,1)$ 时，对应的序列是 $(2,1,5,7,17,31,65,127,\\dots)$。这个序列不包含任何 $4$ 的倍数。因此，$(x,y) = (2,1)$ 满足题目条件。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "另一方面，当 $(x,y) = (3,2)$ 时，对应的序列是 $(3,2,8,12,28,52,108,212,\\dots)$。该序列的第三项是 $8$，它是 $4$ 的倍数。因此，$(x,y) = (3,2)$ 不满足题目条件。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "int vis[N][N];\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tll m, a, b; cin >> m >> a >> b;\n\tll ans = 0;\n\tvar dfs = [&](var dfs, int x, int y)->bool {\n\t\tif (vis[x][y])return vis[x][y] == 2;\n\t\tvis[x][y] = 1;\n\n\t\tll now = a * x + b * y;\n\t\tnow %= m;\n\t\tif (now == 0) {\n\t\t\t// 剪枝，防止爆栈\n\t\t\tvis[x][y] = 2;\n\t\t\treturn 1;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tll nx = now, ny = x;\n\t\tif (dfs(dfs, nx, ny))vis[x][y] = 2;\n\t\treturn vis[x][y] == 2;\n\t\t};\n\tfa(i, 1, m - 1)fa(j, 1, m - 1)ans += dfs(dfs, i, j);\n\tcout << (m - 1) * (m - 1) - ans << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
